Project Description
Nairo is a full managed code HTML Renderer. It aims to be an OpenSource replacement for the WebBrowser control and, in future it will support CSS 1.

Plans for release v0.1
  1. Full implementation of HTML 4.01 Standard

Current State of the Project
  1. p, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5 and h6 are implemented
